		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I watched all 3 parts when the first one was posted here, even though I don't understand russian. But I'm going to re-watch parts 2 and 3 with subtitles of course.
<br />
<br />I could imagine how pissed I would have been if I had bought Super Wonderful Mario (aka Super Mario 5, aka Super Bros 5) as a kid, only to come home and discover that it was Super Mario Bros 2 with a hacked title screen.
<br />
<br />I hope you russians had the ability to try the games in the store before you bought them.

		

