	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">Btw, is there a patch or GG code available that will remove the powerups from a normal copy of Ninja Gaiden / Shadow Warriors? (like in that Dendy version that kinaman showed).</div>
<br />Nevermind, I hacked it myself (for those who want to know, you just need to change the two bytes at file offset 1DA9B-1DA9C from A5 01 to A9 1C).

		

		</td>
	</tr>
