		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">Does it also makes 1up bonus crash the game?</div>
<br />No. My change marks all powerups as immediately taken, so you'll never see any laterns at all. That's not exactly the same as in the Dendy version, but it's the effect I wanted (i.e. no powerups).

		

		</td>
	</tr>
